ruby/jruby notes:

install rvm: curl -L https://get.rvm.io | bash -s stable
rvm install ruby
rvm install jruby
rvm use ruby (or rvm use jruby)

jruby extra notes:

Download the Oracle JCE_Policy lib: http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jce8-download-2133166.html
unzip and read tne README file on instruction.

phantomjs general notes:

download phantomjs and install/copy in a PATH directory.
mac osx can use "brew install phantomjs"

project commandline note:

bundle install
rake db:migrate RAILS_ENV=test
rake spec
rake ci:setup:rspec spec (JUnit style report)

project gradle node:

gradle bundleInstall
gradke rakeDB
gradle rakeSpec
gradle rakeReport (Junit style report)

JUnit style reports are under spec/reports/ directory

